title: Trend's Eyes Like A Doll's Eyes 10/26: Jared Kushner, New York Post, Rubio, World Series, Kazakhstan
itunes:title: Trend's Eyes Like A Doll's Eyes 10/26: Jared Kushner, New York Post, Rubio, World Series, Kazakhstan
description:
On this edition of Trend's Eyes Like A Doll's Eyes Jack and Miles discuss Jared Kushner suggesting Black people don't want to be successful, The New York Post has endorsed Trump, Republicans are saying "we would have been fine" if they went with Marco Rubio, the Dodgers are one game away from a World Series title, and the Kazakhstan tourist board has adopted the "very nice" tag from Borat.
